description:
Support my Sound Design Work and Music Here
https://linktr.ee/zenworld

LFOs are known to create amazing movement and sounds. They are what make or break a sound from basic to expensive-sounding. In today's video, we're going to be going over how you can use LFOs to evolve your sounds, create movement, create sequences, and create even more amazing growls. By the end of this video, you will know how the LFO in Serum 2 works and you will confidently use it to create your own amazing sounds.
